text: This obsoletes IRM 4.11.17, Examining Officers Guide (EOG), Electronically Filed Returns. The information contained in this document is either no longer applicable, or is contained in another

The information in this IRM is either outdated or duplicated in other parts of the IRM. Information can be found in IRM 4.4.23.7.1.2.1, IDRS ELF Requests, and IRM 2.3.73.1, Command Code (CC) TRDBV, or use Employee User Portal (EUP) to access MEF (IMF/BUS) Tax Return information.
